Package: openSparse
Type: Package
Title: GPU computation of sparse matrix
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jiefei Wang
Maintainer: Jiefei Wang <jiefei.wang@roswellpark.org>
Description: The packae intends to utilize the power of GPU to 
  analysis the large sparse matrix. A block operation is implemented 
    to handle the memory issue. A JIT compiler is supported to 
    run the customized kernel on GPU.
